.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.459020574552917e-33, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999278402180926, \"rank\": 7.21649888882235e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old qualified third for the final but then upped the difficulty of his routine during Monday night's team final.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A third straight fourth-placed finish there has added further fuel.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's 100m final - 8:20pm  All eyes will be on the fast Stade de France purple track on Saturday night for the first of this weekend's huge 100m finals.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kate and William try their hand at curling in Stirling  Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Discover a hidden island paradise in the Indian Ocean  We will not know the exact lineup until after the semi-finals on Saturday, but reigning world champion Sha'Carri Richardson of the USA should be a clear favourite barring disaster after her dominant performance in the heats.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"score\": 0.999999966801625, \"rank\": 3.3197929156533275e-08, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\"}, {\"begin\": 2216, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\", \"score\": 0.9999994793289707, \"rank\": 5.205192062842808e-07, \"text\": \"Stirling\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\"}, {\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9758108383657195, \"rank\": 0.024490319033295127, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jamaican rival Shericka Jackson has withdrawn from the 100m event in Paris, but is still running in the 200m.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9458129896474201, \"rank\": 0.05729146347760459, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 2653, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\