rce/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BBC Two briefly pick up the coverage between 6pm and 6:20pm.\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5073, \"end\": 5080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.996505985852786e-27, \"text\": \"BBC Two\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is reduced coverage compared with previous years, when the BBC broadcasted everything from archery to wrestling live on its website or channels.\", \"from\": 5135, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5200, \"end\": 5203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999966087555754, \"rank\": 3.389117524815475e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Discovery+ is the main rights holder forParis 2024and is showing every moment across the Eurosport channels in the UK from 7am to 10.30pm every day.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5410, \"end\": 5412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9933115084563375, \"rank\": 0.006733528692967057, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Live stream:Fans can also catch the BBC coverage live online for free via the BBC Sport website and BBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5481, \"end\": 5484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999966087555754, \"rank\": 3.389117524815475e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398